<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dinner Ordering</title>
    <style>
body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #000000;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #8eb50b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 1em;
        }

        .menu-item {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 1em;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .menu-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .cart {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 1em;
            position: fixed;
            right: 1em;
            top: 1em;
            max-width: 300px;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .cart-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #8eb50b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Dinner Menu</h1>
    </header>

    <section id="menu">
        <!-- Menu items will be dynamically added here using JavaScript -->
    </section>

    <div class="cart" id="cart">
        <h2>Shopping Cart</h2>
        <div id="cart-items">
            <!-- Cart items will be dynamically added here using JavaScript -->
        </div>
        <p>Total: &#8377<span id="total">0.00</span></p>
        <button onclick="checkout()">Checkout</button>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Dinner Ordering</p>
    </footer>
<script>
        // Sample menu data
        const menuData = [
            { id: 1, name: 'Grilled Salmon', description:  'Salmon fillet grilled to perfection, served with lemon </br>and herbs.', price: 15.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 2, name: 'Chicken Alfredo', description: 'Creamy Alfredo sauce with grilled chicken breast over </br>fettuccine pasta.', price: 12.99, imageUrl: "data:image/jpeg;base64,"},
            { id: 3, name: 'Vegetarian Pizza',description: 'Pizza topped with fresh vegetables and cheese.', price: 10.99, imageUrl: "data:image/jpeg;base64," },
            { id: 4, name: 'Beef Stir Fry', description:   'Tender strips of beef with colorful vegetables in a savory</br> stir-fry sauce.', price: 14.99, imageUrl: "data:image/jpeg;base64,"},
            { id: 5, name: 'Caprese Salad', description:   'Fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, and basil drizzled with </br>balsamic glaze.', price: 8.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 6, name: 'Margherita Pizza',description: 'Classic pizza with tomato sauce, cheese, and basil.', price: 11.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
{ id: 7, name: 'Shrimp Scampi', description:   'Shrimp sauted in garlic and butter, served over pasta.', price: 16.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 8, name: 'Vegetable Lasagna',description:'Layers of pasta, ricotta cheese, and mixed vegetables </br>with marinara sauce.', price: 13.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 9, name: 'Teriyaki Chicken', description:'Grilled chicken glazed with teriyaki sauce, served </br>with steamed rice and vegetables.', price: 17.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
            { id: 10, name: 'Caesar Salad', description:   'Crisp romaine lettuce, croutons, and Parmesan </br>cheese tossed in Caesar dressing.', price: 9.99, imageUrl: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,' },
        ];

        const menuSection = document.getElementById('menu');
        const cartItemsContainer = document.getElementById('cart-items');
        const totalElement = document.getElementById('total');
        let cart = [];

       
        menuData.forEach(item => {
            const menuItem = document.createElement('div');
            menuItem.classList.add('menu-item');
            menuItem.innerHTML = `
                <img src="${item.imageUrl}" alt="${item.name}">
                <h2>${item.name}</h2>
                <p>${item.description}</p>
                <p> &#8377 ${item.price.toFixed(2)}</p>
                <button onclick="addToCart(${item.id})">Add to Cart</button>
            `;
            menuSection.appendChild(menuItem);
        });

        
        function addToCart(itemId) {
            const selectedItem = menuData.find(item => item.id === itemId);
            cart.push(selectedItem);
            updateCart();
        }

        
        function updateCart() {
            cartItemsContainer.innerHTML = '';
            let total = 0;

            cart.forEach(item => {
                const cartItem = document.createElement('div');
                cartItem.classList.add('cart-item');
                cartItem.innerHTML = `
                    <p>${item.name}</p>
                    <p> &#8377 ${item.price.toFixed(2)}</p>
                `;
                cartItemsContainer.appendChild(cartItem);
                total += item.price;
            });

            totalElement.textContent = total.toFixed(2);
        }

        
        function checkout() {
            alert('Checkout function triggered!');
            
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>
